title: 12/24/2020 – HOUR 1 – Who Wants James Harden For Christmas? PLUS LaVar Arrington
itunes:title: 12/24/2020 – HOUR 1 – Who Wants James Harden For Christmas? PLUS LaVar Arrington
description:
With Rob Parker and T.J. Houshmandzadeh in for Dan Patrick, the guys weigh in on James Harden’s future as a Houston Rocket! They blast Dwayne Haskins for refusing to take the NFL seriously and speak with fellow Up On Game co-host LaVar Arrington!
